changelog=0.4.9: Fixes task card status when a long scan has already uploaded every file but the queue still reports the active task. Completed file stats now display sync completed instead of staying on syncing.<br>0.4.8: Adds decrypted folder downloads in Decrypt Browse. The app recursively lists encrypted pCloud folders, downloads .pcenc files, decrypts them locally with /data/encryption.key, and returns a zip with the original folder structure.<br>0.4.7: Removes the live upload-speed metric from the Sync Tasks dashboard so the top summary no longer shows a persistent 0 B/s card. The separate pCloud speed test still reports upload/download throughput.<br>0.4.6: Adds a Decrypt Browse tab and Settings key export for encrypted pCloud files.
